data.description: Under $400k! Discover comfort and space in this 5-bedroom, 3-bath Charlotte home, just under 2,500 sqft. A welcoming open concept that starts with the dining room leading into the kitchen, gas fireplace in the living room, a primary level bedroom with a full bath, and a convenient 2-car garage make everyday living a breeze. The vaulted ceiling in the owner's suite adds a touch of elegance, along with a generous walk-in closet. Nestled in a tranquil cul-de-sac with a pond on the other side, this home offers a peaceful retreat. Close to highways I485 & I85 - this home is just minutes from the U.S. National Whitewater Center, airport, and Uptown Charlotte.
